content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 319.309 - Beans with frankfurters in sauce, sauerkraut with wieners and juice, and similar products

State Regulations
"Beans with Frankfurters in Sauce", "Sauerkraut with

Wieners and Juice", and similar products shall contain not less than 20 percent
frankfurters or wieners computed on the weight of the smoked and cooked sausage
prior to its inclusion with the beans or sauerkraut. Notes
